Project description

jaxlib: support library for JAX

jaxlib is the support library for JAX. While JAX itself is a pure Python package,jaxlib contains the binary (C/C++) parts of the library, including Python bindings,the XLA compiler, the PJRT runtime, and a handful of handwritten kernels.For more information, including installation and build instructions, refer to mainJAX README: https://github.com/google/jax/.
